## Interaction Model

### Target Resolution Priority

All actions resolve targets in the following order:

1. Dragged component(s)
2. Selected components
3. Component under cursor
4. No target → no-op

This rule applies uniformly across:
- Keyboard actions,
- Context menu actions,
- Mouse interactions.
```

